to someone else.

24
00:03:03,416 --> 00:03:05,166
Knock-knock...

25
00:03:05,250 --> 00:03:07,416
Hey Naru, whaddup?

26
00:03:09,333 --> 00:03:10,916
Uh... who're you?

27
00:03:11,000 --> 00:03:12,958
Man, lemme tell ya
coming to Shibuya

28
00:03:13,041 --> 00:03:15,000
on a Sunday is crazy.

29
00:03:15,083 --> 00:03:18,541
Mai...! be a sweetheart
and get me an iced coffee.

30
00:03:18,625 --> 00:03:20,625
Uh... no way...

31
00:03:20,708 --> 00:03:22,708
Is that monk in there?

32
00:03:22,791 --> 00:03:25,541
What, the outfit...? I
had a live show today...

33
