she might just be sick?

152
00:08:39,458 --> 00:08:40,958
Because...

153
00:08:41,041 --> 00:08:42,666
she actually said
'I am the white fox

154
00:08:42,750 --> 00:08:44,750
of the harvest god'...

155
00:08:44,833 --> 00:08:47,875
It all happened after
that darn Ouija board...

156
00:08:47,958 --> 00:08:49,291
When everyone was
leaving she told us

157
00:08:49,375 --> 00:08:50,875
that she thought
she was possessed.

158
00:08:50,958 --> 00:08:52,375
I told her that
there was no way,

159
00:08:52,458 --> 00:08:55,416
but she said she
felt really weird.

160
00:08:55,500 --> 00:08:58,125
