and I did a test of courage

172
00:09:26,875 --> 00:09:28,250
in a storage room
in the gym, and

173
00:09:28,333 --> 00:09:29,583
I've been seeing a
bunch of these

174
00:09:29,666 --> 00:09:31,333
weird shadows ever since...

175
00:09:31,416 --> 00:09:33,083
