178
00:09:36,708 --> 00:09:38,416
Yeah...

179
00:09:38,500 --> 00:09:41,250
Um... she said it was like she
all of a sudden couldn't move,

180
00:09:41,333 --> 00:09:43,958
and it felt like someone
was touching her stomach.

