200
00:10:30,083 --> 00:10:31,500
I'm guessing that you're
one of the victims.

201
00:10:31,583 --> 00:10:32,750
Were you involved
in an accident

202
00:10:32,833 --> 00:10:34,791
after sitting at
a certain desk?

203
