288
00:14:37,833 --> 00:14:38,958
Nah not really.

289
00:14:39,041 --> 00:14:40,416
Just kinda
holdin'down the fort.

290
00:14:40,500 --> 00:14:41,791
Oh, I see...

291
00:14:41,875 --> 00:14:44,166
So, how's the
exorcism going?

292
00:14:44,250 --> 00:14:45,958
Well, we've really only
just gotten started...

293
00:14:47,166 --> 00:14:49,166
but I don't think it's
going to be that easy...

294
00:14:49,250 --> 00:14:51,458
there are just so
many cases here.

295
00:14:51,541 --> 00:14:53,875
Yeah, I know... it
really makes you wonder

296
00:14:53,958 --> 00:14:56,083
what's going on
at this school...

297
00:14:56,166 --> 00:14:59,333
curses and ghosts and
supernatural powers...

298
00:14:59,416 --> 00:15:00,916
like, where's the
UFO, you know?

299
00:15:01,000 --> 00:15:02,250
Hold on a second!

300
00:15:02,333 --> 00:15:04,166
supernatural powers?

301
00:15:08,666 --> 00:15:10,416
Did you say
"Kasai Panic?"

302
00:15:10,500 --> 00:15:13,958
Well... There's this rd year
girl named Chiaki Kasai

303
00:15:14,041 --> 00:15:17,041
who could bend a spoon with
just the power of her mind.

304
00:15:17,125 --> 00:15:19,166
It was just after
summer vacation...

305
00:15:19,250 --> 00:15:21,125
suddenly everyone at
school knew her name,

306
00:15:21,208 --> 00:15:23,333
and bending spoons and
other supernatural stuff

307
00:15:23,416 --> 00:15:25,208
became a really big deal.

308
00:15:25,291 --> 00:15:27,375
The school was divided
over the whole thing.

309
00:15:27,458 --> 00:15:30,208
Some people believed in
it, while others didn't.

310
00:15:30,291 --> 00:15:32,666
Then one day Kasai was called
up in front of everyone

311
00:15:32,750 --> 00:15:34,083
during morning assembly...

312
00:15:34,166 --> 00:15:35,833
If you really have
powers, prove it

313
00:15:35,916 --> 00:15:38,083
by bending this
right here and now.

314
00:15:38,166 --> 00:15:39,958
You can't can you?

315
00:15:41,666 --> 00:15:43,083
Whoa, she bent it??

316
00:15:43,166 --> 00:15:46,500
After that, things
got really bad.

317
00:15:46,583 --> 00:15:49,791
A group of teachers started
to attack her credibility.

318
00:15:49,875 --> 00:15:51,541
This is obviously
a trick...

319
00:15:51,625 --> 00:15:53,500
you're just making
fools of us!

320
00:15:53,583 --> 00:15:55,291
I guess that sent Kasai
over the edge,

321
00:15:55,375 --> 00:15:57,458
because then she yelled
back at them...

322
00:15:57,541 --> 00:15:59,916
I'll curse you to death!

323
00:16:00,000 --> 00:16:01,833
And after that, all
of these crazy things

324
00:16:01,916 --> 00:16:04,000
started happening
around school,

325
00:16:04,083 --> 00:16:05,875
like with the desk and
the track locker room.

326
00:16:05,958 --> 00:16:08,375
People started
getting frightened ...

327
00:16:08,458 --> 00:16:11,166
they were saying it had to be
because of Kasai's curse.

328
00:16:11,250 --> 00:16:12,541
I'm almost pretty sure
that's why she hasn't been

329
00:16:12,625 --> 00:16:14,666
coming to class lately...

330
00:16:15,875 --> 00:16:17,500
When she's at school
she's usually hiding out

331
00:16:17,583 --> 00:16:19,416
in the biology
prep room.

332
00:16:19,500 --> 00:16:20,708
I don't blame her...

333
00:16:22,000 --> 00:16:23,625
Yes?

334
00:16:23,708 --> 00:16:25,000
Excuse me...

335
00:16:25,083 --> 00:16:26,916
We're looking for a
Miss Chiaki Kasai.

336
00:16:27,000 --> 00:16:28,916
And may I ask what
this is regarding?

337
00:16:29,000 --> 00:16:32,291
I'm here investigating with
Shibuya Psychic Research...

338
00:16:32,375 --> 00:16:35,708
And I would very much like
to speak with Miss Kasai.

339
00:16:35,791 --> 00:16:38,541
Oh right, um, what
was your name?

340
00:16:38,625 --> 00:16:40,291
My name is
Kazuya Shibuya.

341
00:16:40,375 --> 00:16:41,916
Ahhh...

342
00:16:42,000 --> 00:16:43,333
yes, the principal said
there were going to be

343
00:16:43,416 --> 00:16:45,041
some people coming
to investigate

344
00:16:45,125 --> 00:16:47,458
all the strange things
happening around the school...

345
00:16:47,541 --> 00:16:49,333
It's so good to
meet you both...

346
00:16:49,416 --> 00:16:51,625
please come in, my
name is Kei Ubusuna

347
00:16:51,708 --> 00:16:53,375
and I teach biology here.

348
00:16:53,458 --> 00:16:54,791
Ubusuna...?

349
00:16:54,875 --> 00:16:58,208
That's quite an
unusual name you have.

350
00:16:58,291 --> 00:17:00,333
So you're looking
for Kasai...

351
00:17:00,416 --> 00:17:02,375
I'm guessing you'd like to
ask her about the incident

352
00:17:02,458 --> 00:17:04,583
-this past September?
-Leave me alone!

353
00:17:04,666 --> 00:17:06,291
I have nothing to say!

354
00:17:06,375 --> 00:17:08,208
Kasai I think you should
clear up any confusion

355
00:17:08,291 --> 00:17:10,583
and tell these people
exactly what happened.

356
00:17:10,666 --> 00:17:11,666
Why should I? !

357
00:17:11,750 --> 00:17:14,500
So they can call
me a liar, too? !

358
00:17:14,583 --> 00:17:18,458
But they investigate psychic
phenomena all of the time...

359
00:17:18,541 --> 00:17:20,083
so they're not going
to immediately reject

360
00:17:20,166 --> 00:17:22,041
or laugh at the
things you say.

361
00:17:23,541 --> 00:17:25,916
O-kay... so whaddya
wanna know?

362
00:17:27,416 --> 00:17:30,708
I've heard some very
interesting stories about you

363
00:17:30,791 --> 00:17:32,833
Stories that connect
you to these events...

364
00:17:32,916 --> 00:17:35,416
That you have powers...

365
00:17:35,500 --> 00:17:38,750
The kind of powers that
bend spoons and keys at will.

366
00:17:38,833 --> 00:17:41,083
Those aren't just stories
they're the truth...

367
00:17:41,166 --> 00:17:43,875
I can bend them but I don't
expect you to believe me.

368
00:17:43,958 --> 00:17:45,375
Why wouldn't I?

369
00:17:45,458 --> 00:17:48,000
You're not the only one who
can bend a spoon, you know.

370
00:17:48,083 --> 00:17:50,125
What? ! Can you??

371
00:17:50,208 --> 00:17:51,833
I can...

372
00:17:51,916 --> 00:17:53,708
But even if I couldn't
any psychic researcher

373
00:17:53,791 --> 00:17:54,958
would believe in PK.

374
00:17:59,416 --> 00:18:01,041
Then show me.

375
00:18:02,583 --> 00:18:03,958
I guess I have no choice.

376
00:18:18,166 --> 00:18:19,916
Over summer vacation I
was watching one of those

377
00:18:20,000 --> 00:18:21,791
late night
shows, you know?

378
00:18:21,875 --> 00:18:24,125
This one was about
spoon-bending...

379
00:18:24,208 --> 00:18:26,750
So I got a spoon and
started trying it myself,

380
00:18:26,833 --> 00:18:28,375
and eventually I
learned to do it...

381
00:18:28,458 --> 00:18:30,583
I can't break them
like you, though.

382
00:18:30,666 --> 00:18:32,625
That was in the summer?

383
00:18:32,708 --> 00:18:34,583
But, you Can still
do it. Right ?

384
00:18:34,666 --> 00:18:36,041
Of course!

385
00:18:51,541 --> 00:18:53,958
Stop! Right now!

386
00:18:54,041 --> 00:18:55,208
You were about to
bend the spoon

387
00:18:55,291 --> 00:18:57,458
using the edge of the
chair, weren't you...?

388
00:18:57,541 --> 00:18:58,500
You do realize that

389
00:18:58,583 --> 00:18:59,750
if anyone caught you
doing that trick

390
00:18:59,833 --> 00:19:01,625
they'd never
believe you again.

391
00:19:01,708 --> 00:19:02,708
You're lying...!

392
00:19:02,791 --> 00:19:04,208
I really can
bend a spoon!

393
00:19:04,291 --> 00:19:06,125
Any researcher knows
that psychic abilities

394
00:19:06,208 --> 00:19:08,833
can be affected by
outside sources

395
00:19:08,916 --> 00:19:10,333
and are, therefore, unstable.

396
00:19:10,416 --> 00:19:11,750
When you can't
do something,

397
00:19:11,833 --> 00:19:13,958
it's okay to admit defeat.

398
00:19:14,041 --> 00:19:15,416
The people who will
call you fake

399
00:19:15,500 --> 00:19:17,250
never believe in
you in you anyway,

400
00:19:17,333 --> 00:19:19,208
so don't worry
about what they think.

401
00:19:19,291 --> 00:19:20,958
That's easy for
you to say...

402
00:19:21,041 --> 00:19:22,333
but you don't have
to deal with

403
00:19:22,416 --> 00:19:24,541
how mean people can be
if you can't do it.

404
00:19:24,625 --> 00:19:26,416
