00:19:37,125 --> 00:19:39,208
Then everyone in the
biology club quit.

411
00:19:39,291 --> 00:19:41,916
Saying we must be doing
something crazy or evil...

412
00:19:42,000 --> 00:19:44,625
I don't understand why
this is happening to me...

413
00:19:44,708 --> 00:19:46,416
Is that why you
cursed them?

414
00:19:46,500 --> 00:19:48,583
I'll curse you to death!!

415
00:19:48,666 --> 00:19:50,416
Well, yeah...

416
00:19:50,500 --> 00:19:52,041
I said that but c'mon,

417
00:19:52,125 --> 00:19:55,250
it's not like I could really
do it, could I? !

418
00:19:55,333 --> 00:19:56,625
Right?

