446
00:21:01,250 --> 00:21:03,083
Relax mate. Easy.

447
00:21:03,166 --> 00:21:06,416
You know, Masako's theory
may not be accurate.

448
00:21:06,500 --> 00:21:08,333
Well I'm certain it's
more accurate than yours,

449
00:21:08,416 --> 00:21:09,958
Miss Matsuaki.

450
00:21:10,041 --> 00:21:12,291
In fact, MISS
Matsuzaki, I wonder

451
00:21:12,375 --> 00:21:14,833
